{"tid":908138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擁有4子女1個孫　47歲祖母登男性雜誌百大辣妹榜","createTime":"2018-11-19T11:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T11:51:12.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad66a44b3093c4879a7a95ba72460e782db8ffbd","tid":908138,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"一般形容祖母的詞語不外「和藹」、「慈祥」、「滿頭白髮」等，但澳洲一名祖母斯圖爾特（Gina Stewart）恐怕只能用「火辣」來形容，她更近更榮登雜誌的「2018百大辣妹排行榜」<br />\n47歲的斯圖爾特（Gina Stewart）有4個子女，分別27、25、23和4歲，還有個1歲孫女。<br />\n令她成名的，是與年齡不相稱的火辣外表，早前被網民票選為「全世界最火辣祖母」，最近更登上男性雜誌《美信》（Maxim）「百大澳洲辣妹榜」（Hot 100 Australia List）。對此，她表示「很榮幸能與眾多美麗、有才華和著名的女性並列榜上」。<br />\n斯圖爾特在年初參加《美信》舉辦的選美比賽Miss Maxim 2018，對着其他比她年輕一半的對手，也毫不失色。她經常上傳性感照片，Instagram帳號有12萬人追蹤，尺度非常大膽，挑戰粉絲和Instgram的底線。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099761/org/2eec2d86da13c9a4ee38e937d45d4428.jpg/ZTO2RlboU5e2-M5_ggVI7duKZST33VdSrWfyCK1n8gg?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099761%2Forg%2F2eec2d86da13c9a4ee38e937d45d4428.jpg%2FZTO2RlboU5e2-M5_ggVI7duKZST33VdSrWfyCK1n8gg%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=7224eac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n斯圖爾特（Gina Stewart）已經47歲，有4名子女和一個孫女。<br />\n今年7月斯圖爾特被英國《每日星報》（Daily Star）的網上讀者票選為「全世界最火辣祖母」，斯圖爾特是力壓另外兩名大熱門Carrie Hilton和Alice Vasquez，而以51%的得票率勝出。她非常感謝粉絲們，「知道原來我有這麼多人支持，實在叫我感到不好意思，特別是其他候選女子都那麼美麗動人」。<br />\n年輕時因為胸小而被欺凌<br />\n然而性感是有代價的。看着她豐滿的胸部，你不會料到，斯圖爾特年輕時因為胸小而被欺凌，花1萬美元（約8萬港元）隆胸後，才發現別人總能找到借口挑剔她。「我以為隆了胸，就會無比快樂。現在上圍豐滿了，卻仍然有人說三道四。」<br />\n人人羨慕的外表背後，是對健康的損害。斯圖爾特進行隆胸手術後，患上焦慮症和恐慌症，抑鬱得過去一年只外出了20次，因抵抗力大降而經常生病，又很容易疲倦。為了自己的健康，她決定移除植入物，「粉絲可能會停止追蹤我，並感到失望，我不知道，也不在乎。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099672/org/7c7738d7241c9f6f82602d62f14f1404.jpg/IWhDy5B9F82zvNn_8iZ4NTJ7NMrtE1dXo_5h-KP-Yfg?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099672%2Forg%2F7c7738d7241c9f6f82602d62f14f1404.jpg%2FIWhDy5B9F82zvNn_8iZ4NTJ7NMrtE1dXo_5h-KP-Yfg%3Fv%3Dw480&h=f992b718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099673/org/9b613039c8b53829416cc1fad9c16af0.jpg/9qkzApXFNCq2gL4hyOoUiFB206ySbTGOI8p__CPKf_w?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099673%2Forg%2F9b613039c8b53829416cc1fad9c16af0.jpg%2F9qkzApXFNCq2gL4hyOoUiFB206ySbTGOI8p__CPKf_w%3Fv%3Dw480&h=698852d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2099670/org/79e3bb4c750b4951953d33f75138f270.jpg/-Mae4MfMPJb4Yq5NwX01OAFM0sDp9yj4G-bDMhvmwzI?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2099670%2Forg%2F79e3bb4c750b4951953d33f75138f270.jpg%2F-Mae4MfMPJb4Yq5NwX01OAFM0sDp9yj4G-bDMhvmwzI%3Fv%3Dw480&h=a8138b94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f9d324695c6010961e96e16541e61490426579b","tid":908138,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:17:05.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"8c02dfd72d6c03ddcac50412f9593259b835ffc5","tid":908138,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c507b83b1c0b2a4d18896bf7d450ea9c71ce5ae","tid":908138,"uid":58880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ed6324bbc8e72d356d3959a4d847ebe6992a1f","tid":908138,"uid":55924,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:21:45.000Z","msg":"屌你阿婆！"},{"pid":"012ddf9b4134f6c0b81835b3455cb7e4d1560d32","tid":908138,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T11:29:13.000Z","msg":"最尾幅圖<br />\n隻手好似斷撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089101d833734aca7e0299e8ac0c9edf94e7d524","tid":908138,"uid":145779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-